<section class="section">
  <div class="wrapper">
    <h2 class="section-title">What is Haystack Labs?</h2>
    <div class="grid grid--2col">
      <div class="main-content">
        <p class="text-content">
          Haystack Labs is a one-week experimental program that invites a
          diverse collection of creative professionals from around the world
          to explore the relationship between craft and technology. Over the
          span of the week, participants work on producing new processes,
          tools, machines, and other resources that inform the craft
          community.
        </p>
        <p class="text-content">
          This is not a formal conference or summit, but rather a charrette
          where people intensely collaborate during their time at Haystack
          with the intention of producing projects that fall within the
          craft and technology domain.
        </p>
      </div>
      <div class="sidebar">
        <div class="stats-card">
          <h3 class="stats-title">By the Numbers</h3>
          <div class="stats-grid">
            <div class="stat-item">
              <span class="stat-number">150+</span>
              <span class="stat-label">Participants</span>
            </div>
            <div class="stat-item">
              <span class="stat-number">5</span>
              <span class="stat-label">Years Running</span>
            </div>
            <div class="stat-item">
              <span class="stat-number">40+</span>
              <span class="stat-label">Projects</span>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

